WEBVTT

00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:04.000
[Agent] IT help desk, how can I assist?

00:00:04.500 --> 00:00:08.000
[user] I can't print from the library computer.

00:00:08.500 --> 00:00:18.000
[Agent] Okay, what's your NetID? Actually, let me look up your information first. What's your student number?

00:00:18.500 --> 00:00:22.000
[user] It's 1234567. My NetID is testuser.

00:00:22.500 --> 00:00:28.000
[Agent] Alright, I see your account. Try logging out and back in.

00:00:28.500 --> 00:00:30.000
[user] That didn't work.

00:00:30.500 --> 00:00:35.000
[Agent] Hmm, maybe restart the computer then.

00:00:35.500 --> 00:00:38.000
[user] Still not working.

00:00:38.500 --> 00:00:42.000
[Agent] Not sure what else to try. You might need to contact the library IT directly.

00:00:42.500 --> 00:00:45.000
[user] Okay, I guess I'll do that. Thanks.
